---
title: Le Wagon Middleman boilerplate
---

<div class="welcome text-center padded">
  <h1>Welcome to Middleman</h1>
  <p class="doc">
    <%= link_to "Read Online Documentation", "http://middlemanapp.com/" %>
  </p>
</div>



<div class="banner">
      <div class="banner-content">
        <h1>Bienvenue</h1>
        <p>Vous serez partout chez vous!</p>
        <form class="form-inline">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="exampleInputName2"></label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control input-lg" id="exampleInputName2" placeholder="CheckIn">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="exampleInputEmail2"></label>
            <input type="email" class="form-control input-lg" id="exampleInputEmail2" placeholder="CheckOut">
          </div>
          <select class="form-control input-lg">
            <option>1 personne</option>
            <option>2 personnes</option>
            <option>3 personnes</option>
            <option>4 personnes</option>
          </select>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Chercher</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>


    <!-- Your features code -->
<div class="container">

  <div class="text-center padded features">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
        <%= image_tag "globe.png" %>
        <h2>Découvrez le monde</h2>
        <p>La terre est votre maison.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
        <%=image_tag "dollar.png" %>
        <h2>Payez en ligne</h2>
        <p>Le paiement en cash n'est plus possible.</p>
      </div>


      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
        <%=image_tag "beer.png" %>
        <h2>Rencontrez</h2>
        <p>Découvrez de nouvelles cultures et styles de vie.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
        <%=image_tag "heart.png" %>
        <h2>Partagez et aimez</h2>
        <p>Rejoignez une communauté que vous aimerez.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="wrapper-grey padded">
  <div class="container">
  <h2 class="text-center">Votre prochain voyage</h2>


    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="card" style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url('images/card-brussels.jpeg');">
          <div class="card-category">Bruxelles</div>
            <div class="card-description">
              <h2>Chez Anne</h2>
              <p>Idéalement situé</p>
            </div>
            <% link_to '#' do %>
            <%= image_tag 'anne.jpg', class: "card-user avatar avatar-large" %>
            <% end %>
           <!--  <img class="card-user avatar avatar-large" src="images/anne.jpg"> -->
            <!-- <a href="#" class="card-link" target="_blank"></a> -->
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="card" style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url('images/nath-home.jpg');">
          <div class="card-category">Lille</div>
            <div class="card-description">
              <h2>la maison de Seb</h2>
              <p>Lumineux avec jardin</p>
            </div>
            <% link_to '#' do %>
            <%= image_tag 'seb.jpg', class: "card-user avatar avatar-large" %>
            <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="card" style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url('images/card-paris.jpg');">
          <div class="card-category">Paris</div>
            <div class="card-description">
              <h2>Chez Romain</h2>
              <p>Typique et cosy</p>
            </div>
            <% link_to '#' do %>
            <%= image_tag 'romain.jpg', class: "card-user avatar avatar-large" %>
            <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>


  </div>
</div>


    <!-- Your newsletter code -->

  <div class="text-center padded">
    <h2>Pour recevoir notre newsletter</h2>
      <p>Laissez-nous votre email et recevez nos informations régulièrement</p>
    <form class="form-inline">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="exampleInputEmail2"></label>
        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleInputEmail2" placeholder="nath@example.com">
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">S'abonner</button>
    </form>
  </div>

